return ['x-generator'=>'GlotPress/4.0.1','translation-revision-date'=>'2025-01-04 10:01:21+0000','plural-forms'=>'nplurals=3; plural=(n % 10 == 1 && n % 100 != 11) ? 0 : ((n % 10 >= 2 && n % 10 <= 4 && (n % 100 < 12 || n % 100 > 14)) ? 1 : 2);','project-id-version'=>'Themes - Twenty Nineteen','language'=>'hr','messages'=>['Our 2019 default theme is designed to show off the power of the block editor. It features custom styles for all the default blocks, and is built so that what you see in the editor looks like what you\'ll see on your website. Twenty Nineteen is designed to be adaptable to a wide range of websites, whether you’re running a photo blog, launching a new business, or supporting a non-profit. Featuring ample whitespace and modern sans-serif headlines paired with classic serif body text, it\'s built to be beautiful on all screen sizes.'=>'Naša 2019 izvorna tema je dizajnirana kako bi pokazala prednosti blok uređivača. Predstavlja prilagođene stilove za sve izvorne blokove, i izgrađena je tako da što vidite u uređivaču, to ćete vidjeti na web-stranici. Twenty Nineteen je dizajnirana kako bi bila prilagodljiva širokom spektru web-stranica, bilo da imate foto blog, pokrećete novi posao, ili podržavate neprofitnu organizaciju. Pruža puno praznog mjesta i moderne sans-serif naslove uparene s klasičnim serif fontom teksta, izgrađena je da bude lijepa na svim veličinama zaslona.','Twenty Nineteen'=>'Twenty Nineteen','<span class="primary-text">Next</span> <span class="secondary-text">Comments</span>'=>'<span class="primary-text">Slijedeći</span> <span class="secondary-text">komentari</span>','<span class="primary-text">Previous</span> <span class="secondary-text">Comments</span>'=>'<span class="primary-text">Prethodni</span> <span class="secondary-text">komentari</span>','We help companies communicate with their customers.'=>'Pomažemo tvrtkama u komunikaciji sa svojim kupcima.','Spark interest on social media'=>'Pobudite interes na društvenim mrežama','We help businesses grow.'=>'Pomažemo poduzećima da rastu.','Activate new customers'=>'Aktivirajte nove kupce','We help startups define (or refine) a clear brand identity.'=>'Pomažemo startupima definirati (ili poboljšati) jasan identitet robne marke.','Redefine brands'=>'Redefinirajte marke','What We Do'=>'Što radimo','Oddly enough, Doug Watson also grew up working alongside his parents at a family-owned restaurant in Queens, NY. He &nbsp;worked on digital campaigns for Fortune 500 Companies before joining Eva Green Consulting.'=>'Čudno, Doug Watson također je odrastao radeći uz svoje roditelje u obiteljskom restoranu u Queensu, NY. &nbsp;Radio je na digitalnim kampanjama za Fortune 500 kompanija prije nego što se pridružio Eva Green Consultingu.','Doug Watson'=>'Doug Watson','Eva Young grew up working alongside her parents at their restaurant in Queens, NY. She opened Eva Young Consulting in 2014 to help small businesses like her parents’ restaurant adapt to the digital age.'=>'Eva Young odrasla je radeći uz svoje roditelje u njihovom restoranu u Queensu, NY. Otvorila je Eva Young Consulting 2014. kako bi pomogla malim tvrtkama poput restorana njezinih roditelja da se prilagode digitalnom dobu.','Eva Young'=>'Eva Young','Team'=>'Tim','Content Strategy'=>'Strategija sadržaja','Copywriting'=>'Pisanje teksta','Marketing'=>'Marketing','Social Media'=>'Društvene mreže','Mobile'=>'Mobitel','Website Design'=>'Dizajn web-stranice','Gradient'=>'Prijelaz','Services'=>'Usluge','Contact Us'=>'Kontaktirajte nas','example@example.com'=>'primjer@primjer.com','(555) 555-5555'=>'(555) 555-5555','New York, New York 10023'=>'New York, New York 10023','20 Cooper Avenue'=>'20 Cooper Avenue','Get In Touch'=>'Stupite u kontakt','Learn More'=>'Saznajte više','Eva Young Consulting was founded in 2014 to meet the needs of small businesses in the San Francisco Bay Area. We help startups define a clear brand identity and digital strategy that will carry them through their financing rounds and scale as their business grows. Discover how we can boost your brand with a unique and powerful digital marketing strategy.'=>'Eva Young Consulting osnovana je 2014. kako bi zadovoljila potrebe malih poduzeća na području zaljeva San Francisco. Pomažemo startupima da definiraju jasan identitet robne marke i digitalnu strategiju koja će ih provesti kroz krugove financiranja i proširiti kako njihovo poslovanje bude raslo. Otkrijte kako možemo poboljšati vaš brend jedinstvenom i snažnom digitalnom marketinškom strategijom.','Advocating for Businesses and Entrepreneurs since 2014'=>'Zagovaramo poduzeća i poduzetnike od 2014','About'=>'Informacije','Your comment is awaiting moderation. This is a preview; your comment will be visible after it has been approved.'=>'Vaš komentar čeka moderiranje. Ovo je predpregled; vaš će komentar biti vidljiv nakon što bude odobren.','Dark Blue'=>'Tamno plava','Blue'=>'Plava','Parent post link<span class="meta-nav">Published in</span><br><span class="post-title">%title</span>'=>'<span class="meta-nav">Objavljeno u</span><br><span class="post-title">%title</span>','postFeatured'=>'Istaknuto','Twenty Nineteen requires at least WordPress version 4.7. You are running version %s. Please upgrade and try again.'=>'Twenty Nineteen zahtjeva najmanje inačicu WordPress 4.7. Vi koristite inačicu %s. Nadogradite i pokušajte ponovno.','Back'=>'Povratak','More'=>'Više','Apply a filter to featured images using the primary color'=>'Primjeni filter na istaknutu sliku koristeći primarnu boju.','Apply a custom color for buttons, links, featured images, etc.'=>'Primjeni prilagođenu boju za dugmad, poveznice, istaknute slike, itd.','primary colorCustom'=>'Prilagođeno','primary colorDefault'=>'Izvorno','White'=>'Bijelo','Light Gray'=>'Svjetlo siva','Dark Gray'=>'Tamno siva','XL'=>'XL','Huge'=>'Ogromno','L'=>'L','Large'=>'Veliko','M'=>'M','Normal'=>'Normalno','S'=>'S','Small'=>'Malo','Footer Menu'=>'Izbornik u podnožju','Used before full size attachment link.Full siz